<h1 align="center">LDM @VERSION@</h1><br>

<p align="justify"> The Unidata Local Data Manager (LDM) is a
collection of cooperating programs that select, capture, manage,
and distribute arbitrary data products.  The system is designed for
event-driven data distribution, and is currently used in the <a
href="/projects/idd/index.html">
<b>Unidata Internet Data
Distribution</b></a> (IDD) project. The LDM system includes network
client and server programs and their shared protocols.
The LDM supports flexible, site-specific configuration.

